snippet: D.J. Augustin scored 25 points Saturday night, Joakim Noah had 21 points and 12 rebounds, and the Chicago Bulls turned a possible first-round playoff preview into a laugher, never trailing in a 96-78 win over the Washington Wizards...

headline.print_headline: Bulls Win 5th in a Row, Beat Wizards 96-78
headline.main: Bulls Win 5th in a Row, Beat Wizards 96-78

lead_paragraph: D.J. Augustin scored 25 points Saturday night, Joakim Noah had 21 points and 12 rebounds, and the Chicago Bulls turned a possible first-round playoff preview into a laugher, never trailing in a 96-78 win over the Washington Wizards
